  "about": {
    "title": "Kanz al-Atfal",
    "body": [
      "This app presents <strong>Kanz al-Atfal</strong>, a comprehensive educational book for children and beginners in the creed of Ahl al-Sunnah wal-Jamāʿah.",
      "It contains <strong>1536 questions and answers</strong> across <strong>22 chapters</strong>, covering Tawḥīd, Faith, Fiqh, Biography, and Islamic etiquettes.",
      "Browse chapters, search any question or answer, save favourites, and test yourself with four quiz modes. The app also tracks your weak spots automatically.",
      "The app <strong>works offline</strong> after the first visit — install it to your home screen like a regular app, with no internet required."
